summary: Final comprehensive testing of MOZTEC Money Changer completed successfully. All major features working excellently with 96.2% backend success rate and 95% frontend functionality. Key features tested: Login with admin@moztec.com, Dashboard, Transaction filters, Multi-currency transactions, Customer Member Card profiles with YTD summary, Print KYC, Company Profile settings, Cash Book opening balance, and Mutasi Valas dynamic data calculation.

minor_issues.issue: Single transaction creation returns 200 instead of 201

ui_bugs.issue: Wallet icons for branch balance management not visible in branches table
ui_bugs.impact: Users cannot access branch balance dialog from Settings > Cabang tab, but API works perfectly

passed_tests: Backend: Admin login with admin@moztec.com / admin123
Backend: All 25/26 API endpoints working (96.2% success rate)
Backend: Multi-currency transaction creation and batch voucher generation
Backend: Company settings GET/PUT operations
Backend: Branch balance management APIs
Backend: Transaction filters (branch, currency, date range)
Backend: Customer transactions with YTD summary calculation
Backend: Mutasi Valas dynamic calculation from transactions
Frontend: Dashboard displays correctly with admin authentication
Frontend: Transaction list with filters (branch, currency, date) working
Frontend: Multi-currency transaction toggle checkbox functional
Frontend: Multi-currency transaction add/remove currency items working
Frontend: Transaction purpose field present and functional
Frontend: Customer list with extended columns (JK, Pekerjaan, Alamat)
Frontend: Customer code clickable to open Member Card profile dialog
Frontend: YTD transaction summary in customer profile working
Frontend: Print KYC buttons available (11 found) for customer list
Frontend: Settings > Perusahaan tab - company profile form working
Frontend: Company profile form fields (name, license, address, etc.) functional
Frontend: Cash Book opening balance card visible and working
Frontend: Mutasi Valas dynamic data calculation from transactions working
Frontend: Transaction creation dialog opening and closing properly
Frontend: Navigation between all pages (Dashboard, Transaksi, Data Nasabah, Buku Kas, Mutasi Valas, Pengaturan)
Frontend: Transaction search functionality working
Frontend: Role-based buttons (admin can edit/delete, kasir can reprint)
action_item_for_main_agent: Minor UI fix needed: Add visible wallet icons in the Settings > Cabang tab for accessing branch balance management dialog. The API endpoints work perfectly, but the UI access point (wallet icon with title='Atur Saldo Awal') is not visible to users in the branches table.

success_percentage.frontend: 95% (All major features working, minor wallet icon visibility issue)
